[SN]TITLE[SN]
Premier League: Match reports for Saturday's games

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Read match reports for Saturday's seven Premier League games, as an eighth straight defeat all but relegated Aston Villa and Newcastle also slipped closer to the Championship.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Aston Villa 1-2 Bournemouth
Crystal Palace 1-0 Norwich
Southampton 3-1 Newcastle
Swansea 1-0 Chelsea
Watford 1-1 Everton
Man City 2-1 West Brom
West Ham 3-3 Arsenal
